#Paypal announced its own #Stablecoin yesterday and these are the facts in a nutshell:

- Stablecoin's contract is publicly viewable and written in an outdated version of Solidity.
- It allows the owner (Paypal & Paxos) to stop transactions, freeze addresses and burn funds.
- It also allows administrators to increase the total supply at will.
